Ludum Dare 39 repository
Author: Micah Schuster

Theme: Running out of power

Engine: Unity 5.6
Audio SFX: Audacity
Audio Music: audiotool.com
Sprite Art: Affinity Photo

Game: Operation Lambda

Your power systems are out of alignment, you must realign them before it's too late!
Use the mirrors to align the laser power to the input port.
WASD moves and pushes mirrors
R rotates the mirrors
ESC resets the level


